@startuml
title UC06 - Backend Classes
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
class AdminMatchController {
  +create(dto): MatchDto
  +update(id,dto): MatchDto
  +setEntryGold(id, gold): MatchDto
  +updateResult(id, dto): Response
  +setCriterionResult(criterionId, team): Response
  +cancel(id): Response
}
class MatchService { +validateMatch(dto): void +save(dto): Match +cancel(id): void }
class ScoringService {
  +scoreMatch(matchId): void
  -resolveCriteria(matchId): void
  -computeScores(matchId): List<Participation>
}
class GoldPayoutService {
  +payout(matchId): void
  -pool(entryGold, participants): Decimal
  -winners(participations): List<Participation>
  -splitTwoDecimals(pool, winnerCount): Decimal
}
class NotificationService { +notifyMatchResult(matchId): void +notifyCancelled(matchId): void }
class FootballDataSyncService { +refreshMatches(): SyncResult +scrapeCriterionResults(matchId): void }
class MatchRepository { +save(match): Match +hasRelatedData(id): boolean }
class PredictionRepository { +findByMatch(matchId): List<Prediction> +markCorrectness(matchId): void }
class ParticipationRepository { +upsert(p): MatchParticipation +findByMatch(matchId): List<MatchParticipation> }
class NotificationRepository { +saveAll(list): void }

AdminMatchController --> MatchService
AdminMatchController --> ScoringService
AdminMatchController --> FootballDataSyncService
MatchService --> MatchRepository
ScoringService --> PredictionRepository
ScoringService --> ParticipationRepository
ScoringService --> GoldPayoutService
ScoringService --> NotificationService
GoldPayoutService --> ParticipationRepository
NotificationService --> NotificationRepository

note bottom of ScoringService
  Chạy khi match -> FINISHED (idempotent, 1 lần/trận):
  1. resolveCriteria: set result_team (admin nhập / cào api-football, admin ưu tiên)
  2. computeScores: score = số criterion đúng (+1 mỗi đúng) cho mỗi participant
  3. GoldPayoutService.payout
  4. NotificationService.notifyMatchResult
end note
note bottom of GoldPayoutService
  pool = entry_gold * số participant.
  winners = participant có score cao nhất và >= 1 (hòa -> nhiều người).
  gold_won = pool / winnerCount, làm tròn 2 chữ số thập phân.
  Điểm cao nhất = 0 -> không có winner, pool void.
  Trận < 2 participant -> không tính vào leaderboard (BR29).
end note
note bottom of NotificationService
  FINISHED -> MATCH_WON / MATCH_LOST cho từng participant.
  CANCELLED -> MATCH_CANCELLED + void toàn bộ participation (BR30).
end note
@enduml
